.SS "Administration Overview"
 Administrators are responsible for the deployment, configuration, and maintenance of \fBREADME Template\fP\&. They ensure the system is properly installed, dependencies are satisfied, and documentation is consistently updated\&.
.PP

.br
 
.br
.PP
.PP
.SS "Administration LifeCycle"
 The Administration LifeCycle covers:
.PP
.IP "1." 4
Verifying system prerequisites 
.br

.IP "2." 4
Installing dependencies and the project 
.br

.IP "3." 4
Building and configuring the project 
.br

.IP "4." 4
Generating and maintaining documentation via Doxygen 
.br

.IP "5." 4
Running tests to validate the build 
.br

.IP "6." 4
Managing updates, fixes, and feature integrations 
.br

.IP "7." 4
Monitoring system and project health 
.br

.PP
.PP

